# Pink Canvas Animation (2026 Theme)

An animated canvas-based project featuring floating hearts, bubbles, gradients, and animated text effects.

## 📌 Features

- Canvas API rendering
- Animated floating hearts
- Bubble motion effects
- Gradient background
- Text glow and movement animation
- Continuous animation loop using requestAnimationFrame()

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Canvas API)

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Open the HTML file in a browser.
2. Observe animated hearts, bubbles, and glowing text.

## 🎯 Purpose

This project was created to practice:
- Canvas drawing
- Object animation
- Gradient rendering
- Loop-based animation logic
- Creative visual design

